MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

95-457. State ex rel. Whitmer v. Indus. Comm.

Franklin App. No. 94APD01-59. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Franklin County. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for dismissal be, and hereby is, granted.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this eause.be, and hereby is, dismissed.

Consolidated case No. 95-490, State ex rel. Whitmer v. Indus. Comm., Franklin App. No. 94APD01-59, remains pending.
